### Get All Transactions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Transaction
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/1
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Deposit
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/deposit
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": 1,
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "description": "Salary deposit"
}

### Withdraw
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/withdraw
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": 1,
  "amount": 100.00,
  "description": "ATM withdrawal"
}

### Search Transactions
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/search?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": 1,
  "startDate": "2023-01-01",
  "endDate": "2023-12-31",
  "minAmount": 10.00,
  "maxAmount": 1000.00
}

### Get Recent Transactions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/recent?accountId=1&limit=5&pageable.page=0&pageable.size=5
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Pending Transactions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/pending?accountId=1&pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Cancel Transaction
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Raise Dispute
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/1/dispute
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Unauthorized transaction"
}

### Get Transaction Receipt
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/1/receipt
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Export Transactions
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/export
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": 1,
  "startDate": "2023-01-01",
  "endDate": "2023-12-31",
  "format": "pdf"
}

### Get Transaction Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/statistics?accountId=1
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Transaction Categories
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/categories
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/health
